### ‚ú® New Features
- [`e3b89cc`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/e3b89cc16c98da9d299da221677727cc122af3fa) - Material 3 Expressive design *(PR #125 by @aliernfrog)*
- [`4214ad8`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/4214ad8dae997f382f30a4be9a7c76efbe591ff9) - Redesign list options, items per grid row option *(PR #127 by @aliernfrog)*
- [`8c8c6a6`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/8c8c6a61cc6ab039f63bce599007c37cb7ab8f6d) - Show translation percentages *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`b923b35`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/b923b357bfb3ddf081d75cdca0b99ab2476bfd25) - **Maps**: Improve navigation, redesign map details *(PR #129 by @aliernfrog)*
- [`9b89e57`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/9b89e5729faef58da7d600c13cae6e8074fe3c07) - Ability to cancel indeterminate progress dialogs *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`eeb0277`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/eeb0277844bac282a3443b45ec1a01f365bb3d61) - **Maps**: Option to export to custom location *(PR #130 by @aliernfrog)*
- [`567ca3d`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/567ca3db8b0ee81ad2468df985f57742b0f1f850) - **Maps list**: Button to select/deselect all *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`926c8f9`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/926c8f901f4911549e529003699c103fa0fcd642) - **l10n**: Update translations *(PR #132 by @aliernfrog)*
- [`bc54c29`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/bc54c29aac861f21814fb6ea78db1d921ced7d04) - **Maps list**: Change title to "Maps" from "Pick a map" *(commit by @aliernfrog)*

### üêõ Bug Fixes
- [`cbb2eb9`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/cbb2eb9d38b5abe99e44ffb429fe54ddd4e2e325) - **Maps**: Make sure files are initialized, fix crash when launching with invalid URL *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`5c1c286`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/5c1c28605dd47cdbef2add552c7fdc4e06f65506) - **Maps materials**: Update laclib to remove query parameters from material names *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`247618b`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/247618bc2a11fa7eb768f9e61bb0d50cdce7bc46) - **Maps list**: Remove extra check *(commit by @aliernfrog)*

### ‚ôªÔ∏è Refactors
- [`ba4025f`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/ba4025f7982dd849be46aee3a8368f3c033652c5) - Migrate to navigation3 *(PR #128 by @aliernfrog)*
